  <reg:acttitle>Motor Vehicle Act</reg:acttitle>
  <reg:title>Show Cause Hearings and <in:br/>Reconsiderations Regulation</reg:title>
  <bcl:ccollect value="statreg_vsis_solo"/>
  <reg:content>
    <bcl:section id="d2e29" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Definition</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>In this regulation, <in:term>Act</in:term> means the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96318_00" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Motor Vehicle Act</in:doc></bcl:link>.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e47">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Fees</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e55">
        <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>The fee for a show cause hearing or reconsideration under section 118.97 of the Act is $200, payable by the person applying to show cause or requesting a reconsideration.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e64">
        <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>If the director finds in favour of the person at a show cause hearing or reconsideration, a fee paid under this section by that person must be refunded by the director.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96318_00" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Motor Vehicle Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 318, relevant to the enactment of this regulation: sectionÂ 118.992]</reg:provisionsnote>
  </reg:content>
